reviews: I wear a women’s size eight so I ordered the size that fits up to 8.5. I found it to be an inch at least too big. Loved the design should work ok. Going to the beach next week so not sure how well they’ll stay on in the water.
Ordered based off the photo provided thinking I was getting red and received purple. Didn’t pay enough attention when I ordered to notice that the description and the image didn’t match.
Super soft and very comfortable. Fit was as expected.

These worked out perfect each of our fans was a different colour and these pull strings were the perfect match. We trimmed the strands tog get the perfect length. Super easy and cute. Got them over a month earlier than we thought.

The box was a little banged up but the item was without flaw. Came sooner than anticipated. Took two AA batteries and works great! With enough weight or u can push down gently in the plate. The plate tops the coins into the mouth while playing a short tune. Very easy to get the change out the bottom.

Item is just as described. Super absorbent. We have less issues with the cats moving it around the room like the last one so I’d say the rubber bottom is pretty good. Smaller than I thought but I suck with dimensions. Haven’t had to clean it yet but that is one of the key reasons we bought a new mat
Got these for our cat as he always managed to get out of the others. I’ve noticed he’s not trying to get this one off or scratching around his neck a lot. Great value
Love how our tags turned out! Enough room on the back for our single line address and both our cell numbers. Shipping took a bit but it was coming from the states and it is a pandemic.

review_title: Applicator is great, screen is bubbling
reviews: Installed very easy so impressed. After almost a month I started getting some bubbling up around the edges. I have two more that when it really bugs me I’ll replace it.
Case is cute and pretty sturdy. All the tools makes prepping my nails for a manicure super easy. Where have cuticle scissors been my whole life??!! Game changer!

review_title: Great colour don’t forget the top coat
reviews: Gorgeous colour! I found it didn’t cure great with my lamp. Bought the Aimeili top coat and it cured amazing. Make the investment and make sure you have the top coat as well!
Curtains were exactly what I expected. The “greyish white” description is very accurate. Darkens the room very well which is surprising for such a light colour. They’re fairly thick.

review_title: My cat got out of it easy
reviews: Not sure about your cat but mine is liquid he can slide right out of this harness and we adjusted it to be snug. This hardness would probably be better for dogs
Should have bought these years ago! They are sturdy that I feel like they’re gonna last a long while.

Bathing suit shopping as a plus size women always sucks. I’m 5’5” 230lbs. The bust was a little overflowing normally a 38DD. The bottoms fit fine. Overall it’s as flattering as I expected for my size. Definitely a fun design and print. Overall happy. Btw why don’t they see the bra liners in why are they always separate?!

review_title: Not sturdy not for every day
reviews: Everything was great until one of the pins broke and I almost lost my watch in a field at work
Works great with my fire tablet and my iPhone 11
Love these brushes! The only way I can brush my hair when wet. Everyone should own one of these brushes!

Wish it came with an extra battery. Followed the washing procedures and had some fires on the left side of the chest get all tangled not sure how to fix that. The right side of the chest and back are working great. Definitely takes the chill out of you.

review_title: Very bright, works great, can fall off
reviews: Flashlight works great. Battery lasts for hours. The telescoping is great for seeing reflective objects from a mile away. Downside is the clip does release sometimes so it can fall off of you if you are being very physical while wearing it
Love these. Keeps my hair from attacking me or my partner at night. Stays well on my head but possibly too large for most people unless u have a lot of hair

review_title: Works well at collecting hair in my tub
reviews: Fit loosely in my tub drain. Hair does get trapped in it easy. Hair is relatively easy to take out of the plug. It does not suction at all.

review_title: First switch screen perfect. Easy to install.
reviews: You get two in the pack. Surprisingly put the first one one in with no trouble, no bubbles and no dust under the screen cover. Fit the screen perfectly. Very happy. Kit includes 2: dust wipes, screen cleaner, tabs to help you line the screen up and two screen covers.

review_title: Fit well and makes switch feel sturdier
reviews: Definitely makes me feel my switch is sturdier in my hands. Fit well over my switch.
This isn’t as cheap as other kinds from this brand, but it covers the odours a lot better! So if you have a smaller space I’d recommend this product over the others.
I know it’s weird to have a preferred colour of hi lighters but I was thrilled to find a pack of just green!

review_title: Stays put, nice to stand on
reviews: I hated my boyfriends shower mat! This one is 1000x better! It’s large it almost covers the whole base of the tub, it stays in place and doesn’t move, and it also has a comfortable texture on your feet.
Who hasn’t lost these things in a move? Went to put my curtain rods up and I couldn' find the brackets. They work well with my old curtain rods colour matches. Very happy

Bought for my boyfriend and myself. Absolutely comfortable! Pockets are so large my switch fits in it! Also has thumb holes! We both love the onesies. They are not fleece so we can wear them for more than just winter
5’11” 215lbs XL fits well
5’5” 230lbs XXL has lots of room especially in the legs
The seller is also great with communication would buy from them again!

LOVE these capris! Passed the see through bend test with flying colours! The fabric is so soft and comfortable I wish I had these in every length and colour. Pocket fits my iPhone 11. Would definitely buy again.
5’5” 230lbs XXL fit great. Not tight feeling.

Gorgeous cross stitch can not wait to finish the one I’m on to start this one! I only buy Dimensions for my cross stitching because the kits are so easy and well organized that you can focus on the joy of stitching.

review_title: More colours, smaller size with a smaller price
reviews: Have you ever used a pencil crayon until it was too short to use? I haven’t so I jumped at the idea of more colours and smaller size! Honestly they would be fantastic for kids! Personally I need more hobbies to get me through Covid19 so drawing has become one of them! Cheers!
Hard like shell case fits my switch with its personal case on. Great for travelling. I feel much more secure with my switch in my backpack now.
Doing some projects and needed some material we could use for stencils in our cricut. This made great sense do to the price of the product to use.

My moms touch pad stopped working for her computer and because of social distancing I can’t help he fix it. She has next to no computer ability at all, she plugged it in and it started working again. She is happy.

Not as cheap as Petsmart, ordered it because Petsmart wasn’t doing curb side pick up during the start of the pandemic and we were running low. Otherwise it is the exact same wet food we feed our cat every day and he loves it.
Wish I bought a bigger bag these are amazing! I don’t have a sweet tooth but I could eat this whole bag in one sitting!
I didnt realize how large the bag was when I bought it! They are very tasty, I do find them a touch too sweet but I’m not hugely fond of sweets. Would buy then again though.

review_title: Exactly what I was looking for
reviews: Exactly what u was liking for! Making a family cook book and my Qcards fit perfectly!
Holds my gloves well, if you’re working strenuously sometimes it can get unclipped from my pocket

review_title: Cute! But too thick to wirelessly charge
reviews: Loved the design and the glow in the dark feature. Case is too thick to wirelessly charge through and too thick to support my magnet car mount

review_title: Fits my XL head! Finally a one size fits all that does!
reviews: Finally a hat that fits my XL head! When companies say one size fits all, they’re normally lying. This hat fits. Keeps my head fairly warm in the fall weather probably too light for the negative weather in Ontario.

review_title: Cute, comfortable and fits larger than expected
reviews: First ordered as an XXL and it was too big could fist material at my waist. Returned and ordered the XL which fit a touch loose in the waist but perfect/tight in the arms. The dress is super cute on, I found the colour to be more vibrant in person I would say wine red not burgundy. Purchased for fall photos, Christmas dinner and a friends wedding in January. Pretty easy to dress it up or down for what ever occasion.
My favourite shampoo. Gets my hair and scalp squeaky clean which is fantastic as I have an oily scalp. Cheaper on amazon and always in stock. Can be hard to find in my town.

Measured myself and decided to go with this size and I was swimming in the coveralls. I’m 5’5” and around 240lbs and these are definitely made for someone a foot taller and much heavier. I ordered a similar one from Carhartt through amazon and got the XXL short and it fits perfect with room to layer. Carhartt needs better sizing charts.

I wish the screen cover itself would cover more of my phone face. It does just fit the screen itself. It was fairly easy to install but like a dummy I installed it without the screen being lit and I had to readjust the screen cover a few times to get it straight and in stuff with a little fuzz now stuck on the underside of my screen.

Love how my phone can magnetize into my wallet and the case on the phone is pretty sturdy. I find on the wallet case the outer framing around the camera section to be very flimsy not very reinforced. Otherwise love the case, the phone case magnet is compatible for the magnet holders in my car for my phone which is half the reason I chose this style.

review_title: Fits big and tall. Lots of room for mobility
reviews: I’m 5’5” 240lbs normally a size 18, ordered the XXLshort, they’re perfect. Can totally layer under them, plenty of room and mobility which is key for my job. Initially ordered the 3XL (based off my measurements) thinking it would be just a touch loose, instead I looked like a toddler wearing their parents clothing. Returned that pair and got the XXL short and I’m very happy. Can’t wait for colder weather to whip these babies out!

The magnet of pretty strong, works great for travelling and having rental vehicles because you can take it with you. Doesn’t really seat well in my car because my vents are too recessed. Otherwise great product

review_title: Loved them just not with the iPhone 11
reviews: Absolutely loved this with my iPhone 6S. Got the new iPhone 11 it will not pair. It’s a known issue with the newest iPhones and this model.

This models buttons were very recessed which made it difficult to use at work where I’m required to wear a watch. It was nice because it wasn’t as big as other gshocks. I didn’t use it long returned it.
No more questioning if the dishwasher has clean or dirty dishes. Easy to use and attaches itself securely to my dishwasher
My prescription safety glasses are so old the protective rubber arms have worn off. These were easy to install and made my glasses much more comfortable to wear and less likely to slip off

review_title: Fantastic, works well for attaching to side of nightstand
reviews: Love it! Attached it to the side of my night stand so I don’t have to stick it to the top surface. The magnetism from the charging doggle keeps the watch on the charging base. 100% happy with this purchase.
Can’t wear them for too long as they irritate my ears. They have a good appearance
I prefer the braided cord over the regular type. Really like the extra reinforcement on this product where the cord meets the end portions. Much stronger than the previous models.
After over 2 decades of torture brushing my hair after a shower (no amount of leave in conditioner would work) this brush has revolutionized my experience. I will never buy another brush ever.
Love the design! The shower curtain is a heavier weight so it doesn’t billow or stick to you in the shower.
Love the speaker! Easy to use, great sound and fantastic price. Also love the colour
Love the replacement bands they’re fantastic. Very similar to the stock one that came with my fit bit.
Cable quality is good. Hopefully it will last longer than my iPhone cable.
Arrived ahead of time, and works with my tv! Thank you!!
Love it coming along nicely!!
Received the album and found that it was warped and rocked in my record player. Just received a replacement record fairly quickly and I'm hoping that it is good.
Very good story, entertaining believable characters and yes very steamily detailed! I Will definitely be reading more from this author.
